{"format":"tiptap/v1","updatedAt":"2026-06-22T12:43:58.638Z","doc":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Random Search is a "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"stochastic hyperparameter tuning technique"},{"type":"text","text":" that randomly samples a fixed number of hyperparameter combinations from a predefined search space, evaluating each to find the best-performing set—often achieving comparable results to Grid Search with far fewer trials."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"What it is"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Instead of exhaustively testing every combination (like Grid Search), Random Search:\n- Defines "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"ranges or distributions"},{"type":"text","text":" for each hyperparameter (e.g., learning rate ∈ [0.001, 0.1], layers ∈ {2, 4, 6, 8})\n- Randomly samples "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"one combination at a time"},{"type":"text","text":" from these distributions\n- Runs for a "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"fixed number of iterations"},{"type":"text","text":" (e.g., 50 random trials) rather than testing all combinations"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"For example, with the same hyperparameters from Grid Search:\n- Learning rate: {0.01, 0.1, 0.5}\n- Number of hidden layers: {2, 4}"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Random Search might sample:\n- Trial 1: (0.01, 4), Trial 2: (0.5, 2), Trial 3: (0.1, 4),... up to your iteration limit"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Why it matters in Generative AI Core Architectures"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Generative AI models (Transformers, GANs, diffusion models) have "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"high-dimensional hyperparameter spaces"},{"type":"text","text":" where Grid Search becomes infeasible. Random Search excels here because:"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Generative AI Hyperparameter"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Typical Search Range"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Learning rate"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[0.0001, 0.01] (continuous)"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Hidden dimension"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{256, 512, 768, 1024, 2048}"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Number of layers"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{6, 8, 12, 16, 24}"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Attention heads"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{4, 8, 12, 16}"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Batch size"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{16, 32, 64, 128}"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Temperature"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[0.5, 1.5] (continuous)"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"With 6 hyperparameters and 5 values each, Grid Search needs "},{"type":"inlineMath","attrs":{"latex":"5^{6} = 15,625"}},{"type":"text","text":" models. Random Search can find good configurations with "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"50–100 trials"},{"type":"text","text":" instead."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"How it works (step-by-step)"}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":1,"type":null},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Define search space"},{"type":"text","text":": Specify hyperparameters and their ranges/distributions"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- Continuous: use uniform or log-uniform distributions (e.g., "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"learning_rate ∈ uniform(0.001, 0.1)"},{"type":"text","text":") - Discrete: use lists (e.g., "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"layers ∈ {2, 4, 6, 8}"},{"type":"text","text":")"}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":1,"type":null},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Set iteration count"},{"type":"text","text":": Choose how many random combinations to sample (e.g., 60 trials)"}]}]}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":1,"type":null},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Sample randomly"},{"type":"text","text":": For each iteration:"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- Draw one value for each hyperparameter from its distribution - Create a complete combination"}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":1,"type":null},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Train and evaluate"},{"type":"text","text":": Train the model with that combination and measure performance on validation set"}]}]}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":1,"type":null},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Repeat"},{"type":"text","text":": Continue for all iterations"}]}]}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":1,"type":null},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Select best"},{"type":"text","text":": Return the hyperparameter set with the highest validation score"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The key insight: "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"not all hyperparameters are equally important"},{"type":"text","text":". Random Search explores a wider range of values for critical parameters, often finding good configurations faster."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Benefits"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Advantage"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Why it matters for Generative AI"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Much faster"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"60 random trials vs. 15,000+ grid points—saves weeks of GPU time"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Scales to high dimensions"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Works well with 10+ hyperparameters where Grid Search fails"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Broader exploration"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Samples from entire ranges, not just discrete points—can discover optimal continuous values "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"https://h2o.ai/wiki/grid-search/","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer nofollow","class":"text-brand-600 underline dark:text-brand-400","title":null}}],"text":"h2o"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Simple to implement"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Just random sampling—no complex optimization logic"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Parallelizable"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Each trial is independent—run across multiple GPUs"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Often matches Grid Search"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Studies show 60 random points often find as-good-or-better configurations"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Trade-offs and limitations"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Limitation"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Impact"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"No optimality guarantee"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Might miss the true best combination (probabilistic, not exhaustive)"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Requires iteration tuning"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Must choose how many trials—too few = poor search, too many = wasted compute"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Can repeat combinations"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"With discrete values, may sample the same combination multiple times (sampling with replacement)"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Less predictable"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Results vary between runs; harder to reproduce exactly without fixing random seed"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Grid Search vs. Random Search comparison"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Dimension"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Grid Search"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Random Search"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Search strategy"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Exhaustive (all combinations)"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Stochastic (random sampling)"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Number of trials"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"inlineMath","attrs":{"latex":"\\prod n_i"}},{"type":"text","text":" (exponential)"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Fixed (e.g., 50–100)"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Computational cost"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Very high (days/weeks for LLMs)"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Low (hours/days)"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"High-dimensional spaces"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Fails (too many combinations)"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Works well"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Continuous hyperparameters"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Must discretize (loses precision)"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Samples continuous distributions directly"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Optimality guarantee"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Yes (within grid)"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"No (probabilistic)"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"When to use"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Few hyperparams (2–4), narrow ranges"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Many hyperparams (5+), broad ranges"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A key research finding: "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"trying 60 random points sampled from the grid seems to be good enough"},{"type":"text","text":" for most cases, often matching or beating Grid Search with far fewer evaluations."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"When to use Random Search in Generative AI"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Use Random Search when:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- You have "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"5+ hyperparameters"},{"type":"text","text":" to tune (common in Transformers)\n- Search spaces are "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"broad"},{"type":"text","text":" (e.g., learning rate from 0.0001 to 0.01)\n- Training is "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"expensive"},{"type":"text","text":" (LLMs take days per run)\n- You need "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"quick baselines"},{"type":"text","text":" before deeper optimization"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Use alternatives when:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- You have "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"2–4 hyperparameters"},{"type":"text","text":" with narrow ranges → Grid Search may be fine\n- You need "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"fine-tuned optimization"},{"type":"text","text":" after random search → Use Bayesian Optimization\n- Resource is unlimited and you want guaranteed optimality → Grid Search (but rarely practical)"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Practical example in code (scikit-learn)"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"python"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"from sklearn.model_selection import RandomizedSearchCV\nfrom scipy.stats import uniform, randint\n\nparam_distributions = {\n    'learning_rate': uniform(0.001, 0.01),  # Continuous uniform distribution\n    'num_layers': randint(2, 10),            # Integer distribution\n    'hidden_dim': [256, 512, 768, 1024],    # Discrete list\n    'batch_size': randint(16, 128)\n}\n\nrandom_search = RandomizedSearchCV(\n    estimator=your_generator_model(),\n    param_distributions=param_distributions,\n    n_iter=60,                   # 60 random trials\n    cv=5,                        # 5-fold cross-validation\n    n_jobs=-1,                   # Parallel across all CPUs\n    random_state=42              # Reproducibility\n)\n\nrandom_search.fit(X_train, y_train)\nbest_params = random_search.best_params_"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Key differences from Grid Search:\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"param_distributions"},{"type":"text","text":" instead of "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"param_grid"},{"type":"text","text":" (uses distributions/lists)\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"n_iter=60"},{"type":"text","text":" specifies trial count instead of exhaustive combinations"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Random Search strategies for better performance"}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":1,"type":null},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Log-uniform sampling for learning rates"},{"type":"text","text":": Use logarithmic distribution since learning rates often work best in orders of magnitude (0.001, 0.01, 0.1)"}]}]}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":1,"type":null},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Two-stage approach"},{"type":"text","text":":"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- Stage 1: Random Search with 50–100 trials to find promising region - Stage 2: Grid Search or Bayesian Optimization around that region for fine-tuning"}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":1,"type":null},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Sample without replacement for discrete values"},{"type":"text","text":": Avoids repeating the same combination"}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Key takeaways"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Random Search is "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"stochastic and efficient"},{"type":"text","text":"—randomly samples fixed iterations instead of exhaustive search"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"It's "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"much faster than Grid Search"},{"type":"text","text":" (60 trials vs. thousands) while often achieving similar or better results"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Works "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"exceptionally well in high-dimensional spaces"},{"type":"text","text":" where Grid Search becomes infeasible"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Handles "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"continuous hyperparameters naturally"},{"type":"text","text":" by sampling from distributions (no discretization needed)"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"For "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Core Architectures in Generative AI"},{"type":"text","text":", it's the "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"practical default"},{"type":"text","text":" for initial tuning—most production LLM pipelines start with Random Search before refined optimization"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"No optimality guarantee"},{"type":"text","text":", but empirically effective for finding good configurations quickly"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Random Search is particularly valuable for your work as a Full Stack Engineer in Gen AI because it "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"reduces compute costs dramatically"},{"type":"text","text":" while still delivering strong model performance—essential when training large transformers or diffusion models on cloud GPUs."}]}]}}
